OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776477807
OL,3,CFormer BBC DJ and Live Aid presenter
OL,4,CAndy Kershaw dies aged 66
OL,6,FFormer BBC DJ and Live Aid presenter
OL,7,FAndy Kershaw has died aged 66, his
OL,8,Ffamily has told the BBC.
OL,10,FIt was revealed in January that
OL,11,FKershaw was undergoing cancer
OL,12,Ftreatment after tumours which were
OL,13,Fseverely limiting his mobility were
OL,14,Fdiscovered in his spine last August.
OL,16,FThe DJ spent almost three decades
OL,17,Fworking for the BBC, and was best
OL,18,Fknown for his Radio 1 show which ran
OL,19,Ffrom 1985 to 2000.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
