PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776477807
OL,3,CFormer BBC DJ and Live Aid presenter
OL,4,CAndy Kershaw dies aged 66
OL,6,FKershaw also travelled across the
OL,7,Fworld to cover conflicts and cultural
OL,8,Fstories for the BBC, contributing to
OL,9,FRadio 4 shows including From Our Own
OL,10,FCorrespondent, the Today programme and
OL,11,FThe World Tonight.
OL,13,FHis coverage included the 1994 Rwandan
OL,14,Fgenocide, and reporting from Sierra
OL,15,FLeone in 2001 during the final stages
OL,16,Fof its civil war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
