PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776477807
OL,3,CFormer BBC DJ and Live Aid presenter
OL,4,CAndy Kershaw dies aged 66
OL,6,FThe Rochdale-born broadcaster received
OL,7,Fmultiple Sony Radio Academy Awards
OL,8,Fthroughout his career, and was
OL,9,Fcelebrated for bringing world music
OL,10,Fand specialised genres to mainstream
OL,11,Fradio.
OL,13,FThe veteran DJ joined BBC Radio 3 in
OL,14,F2001 but left the post in 2007, having
OL,15,Ffaced a series of personal problems
OL,16,Fafter his long-term relationship broke
OL,17,Fdown and he was jailed after breaking
OL,18,Fa restraining order.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
