PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776477807
OL,3,CFormer BBC DJ and Live Aid presenter
OL,4,CAndy Kershaw dies aged 66
OL,6,FKershaw was in a 17-year relationship
OL,7,Fwith Juliette Banner, and the pair had
OL,8,Ftwo children together.
OL,10,FThe couple lived on the Isle of Man
OL,11,Ftogether before eventually separating.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
