PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776477807
OL,3,CFormer BBC DJ and Live Aid presenter
OL,4,CAndy Kershaw dies aged 66
OL,6,FHe later returned to the BBC in 2010
OL,7,Fto host its Music Planet programme
OL,8,Falongside Lucy Duran, and again in
OL,9,F2020 for a brief stint on Radio 3
OL,10,Fpresenting The Kershaw Tapes.
OL,12,FKershaw continued his career as a
OL,13,Fbroadcaster in recent years, having
OL,14,Flaunched his own podcast which
OL,15,Ffeatured guests such as Robyn
OL,16,FHitchcock, The Burner Band and Martin
OL,17,FCarthy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
