PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776477807
OL,3,CFormer BBC DJ and Live Aid presenter
OL,4,CAndy Kershaw dies aged 66
OL,6,FHe revealed his cancer diagnosis in a
OL,7,Fstatement earlier this year, and said
OL,8,Fhe was in "good spirits", joking he
OL,9,Fwas "determined not to die before
OL,10,FBenjamin Netanyahu, Vladimir Putin,
OL,11,FDonald Trump and Ant'n'Dec".
OL,13,FHis sister Liz is also a broadcaster
OL,14,Fand is one of the longest serving
OL,15,Ffemale national radio DJs in the UK,
OL,16,Fhaving had a tenure at the BBC for
OL,17,Fmore than 30 years.
OL,19,FCatch up on the latest entertainment
OL,20,Fnews with ITV's Unscripted podcast
OL,21,Fwith Nina Nannar
